jpg" alt="Script style engraving" width="150" height="65" /></a> <a href="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/engrave-mb_l.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-15" title="Block Style Engraving" src="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/engrave-mb_l-150x67.jpg" alt="Block style engraving" width="150" height="67" /></a>\r\n<h3>Shipping Charges</h3>\r\nThe shipping cost depends on the value of each ring. Shipping through the post office is the least expensive, about $11 to a U. S. address for rings valued at up to $200. Shipping with tracking is also available through 2-day UPS or FedEx for about $16, to a U. S. address. International rates available upon request. <strong>Tell us the value of your ring and how you would like it shipped and we’ll give you the exact shipping charge.</strong>\r\n\r\n» <a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="../order-a-resizing"><strong>Request a price quote for your titanium ring.</strong></a>', 'We Can Resize Your Titanium Ring!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2012-02-14 17:27:31', '2012-02-15 00:27:31', '', 4, 'http://titaniumresizing.com/4-revision-13', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp_trs_posts` VALUES (38, 1, '2010-10-04 12:22:24', '2010-10-04 19:22:24', 'Have a question or comment for Exotica Jewelry or Chris and Sandy Boothe? Please contact us using the form below. You can also contact us at the following address and phone numbers:\r\n<blockquote style="background-image:none;">Exotica Jewelry\r\nPO Box 9\r\nClarkdale, AZ 86324\r\n\r\nToll-free: (800) 297-6707\r\nInternational: +1 (928) 634-5307</blockquote>\r\nIf you would like a price quote for your resizing or are ready to place an order, please use our <a title="Place an order or get more information" href="/order-a-resizing">order form</a>.\r\n\r\n<!--cforms name="Contact Exotica Jewelry"-->', 'Contact Exotica Jewelry', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-2', '', '', '2010-10-04 12:22:24', '2010-10-04 19:22:24', '', 11, 'http://titaniumresizing.com/11-revision-2', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
INSERT INTO `wp_trs_posts` VALUES (39, 1, '2012-03-20 10:28:39', '2012-03-20 17:28:39', '<strong>Have you decided you want to get your titanium ring resized? </strong>Because each titanium ring is custom-sized, we need more information before we can give you an exact cost. Just fill out the short form below and we\'ll respond with a price quote and more information. <em>Submitting this form does <strong>not</strong> obligate you to order from us.</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Please note that we may not be able to resize titanium rings with tension-set stones.</strong> All rings receive complimentary inside-ring engraving.\r\n\r\n<strong>To begin your titanium ring resizing order, email us at <a href="mailto:info@titaniumresizing.com ">info@titaniumresizing.com </a>or call us at (800) 297-6707.</strong> Things to mention:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Whether you want your ring sized larger or smaller</li>\r\n	<li>Whether your ring has gemstones</li>\r\n	<li>If you would like a complimentary inside-ring engraving, the text of that engraving (you may also submit this later)</li>\r\n	<li>Any other questions or comments you have</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Order a Resizing', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-3', '', '', '2012-03-20 10:28:39', '2012-03-20 17:28:39', '', 12, 'http://titaniumresizing.com/12-revision-3', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
